Write a JAVA Program to check wheter a person is eligible for a driving license based on age:
public class DrivingLicenseEligibility {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int age = 18;

        if (age >= 18) {
            System.out.println("The person is Eligible for Driving License");
        } else {
            System.out.println("Not Eligible for Driving License");
        }
    }
}

OUTPUT:
The person is Eligible for Driving License
